title: Ezekiel Elliott and Jared Goff's Contract Extensions
itunes:title: Ezekiel Elliott and Jared Goff's Contract Extensions
description:
Colin comments on the Ezekiel Elliott’s contract extension, why it’s still Dak Prescott’s team, and why he prefers how the Rams do business. Guests include Jane Slater, Nick Wright, Joel Klatt, Frank Caliendo, and Bucky Brooks.
